{"tid":1866530,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"海之戀「睇樓送10個口罩」 成交送300個","createTime":"2020-02-06T19:07:09.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-11T00:01:17.000Z","uid":28765,"like":18,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"8286226be3f6a5f71debfa336e85eb4881b08f54","tid":1866530,"uid":28765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-06T19:07:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://appledaily-hk-appledaily-prod.cdn.arcpublishing.com/resizer/K98xvC7X8nI2hBjNT58B2zkiDYA=/802x1738/arc-photo-appledaily.s3.amazonaws.com/ap-ne-1-prod/public/Z5FFPAK6YQS6C6HOTAPNFSWB4U.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fappledaily-hk-appledaily-prod.cdn.arcpublishing.com%2Fresizer%2FK98xvC7X8nI2hBjNT58B2zkiDYA%3D%2F802x1738%2Farc-photo-appledaily.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fap-ne-1-prod%2Fpublic%2FZ5FFPAK6YQS6C6HOTAPNFSWB4U.jpg&h=9aac41c2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n市場瘋傳海之戀睇樓送口罩放盤。<br />\n<br />\n【新增美聯回應】昔日窮人恩物，今日買樓送口罩。近期樓市受到肺炎肆虐下交投淡靜，地產代理難以開單維持生計。繼荃灣樂悠居「窮人恩物」後，AA再發揮抽水本色，港人一罩難求下，有地產代理在網上推銷荃灣海之戀二手放盤，「睇樓送10個口罩」，「成交即送300個」。<br />\n<br />\n今日市場瘋傳海之戀一個二手放盤，實用面積531方呎的單位，開價898萬元，呎價接近萬七。吸睛之處，不是圖中的全海景，而是「睇樓送10個口罩」，「成交即送300個」。在目前全球鬧口罩荒下，代理為促成交易，睇樓送口罩的確有得諗。該圖片印有美聯物業水印，本報向美聯查詢睇樓及買樓是否真的送口罩，該公司回應指一向要求員工發放準確資訊。<br />\n<br />\n監管局：從業員應言出必行<br />\n<br />\n地產代理監管局提醒地產代理，在宣傳物業時，切記不可發放內容失實或具誤導性的廣告。作為專業的地產代理，執業時應保持言出必行，兌現曾給予客戶的承諾，否則會損害行業聲譽，有機會被監管局處分。<br />\n<br />\n本報再於搵樓網28Hse搜尋有關「口罩」的放盤資料，紅磡半島豪庭亦有單位「睇樓送口罩」，屯門瓏門一個叫價850萬元的661方呎放盤單位，標題寫上「國難當前，套現買口罩」。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.finance.appledaily.com/finance/20200206/4HWAEIZTXPR3FAGL7YUZR6GO4A/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.finance.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2F20200206%2F4HWAEIZTXPR3FAGL7YUZR6GO4A%2F&d=zpo3oWyV3xTDIRTZ1PVZWZbpPLVkgxcsq72qYZiHPFQ%3D&h=d10e24d2\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.finance.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2F20200206%2F4HWAEIZTXPR3FAGL7YUZR6GO4A%2F&h=3b1645fb\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.finance.appledaily.com/finance/20200206/4HWAEIZTXPR3FAGL7YUZR6GO4A/</a>"},{"pid":"bcaf540d4174d90e294df21420cb86a225796c7c","tid":1866530,"uid":42215,"like":53,"dislike":1,"score":52,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-06T19:15:30.000Z","msg":"睇三十次等於成交<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d6310748b7c260f3041b0aacf86649cd9d701a8b","tid":1866530,"uid":202872,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-06T19:19:30.000Z","msg":"連登冇口罩既識做啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/smile3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"27526303bc0ef1ddacfa3c0c85d1c85c8f44c440","tid":1866530,"uid":207122,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-06T19:20:06.000Z","msg":"睇又唔洗錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f3e8d7e360d2a7aca6db1234525155f75e495209","tid":1866530,"uid":66365,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-06T19:34:26.000Z","msg":"送三百個等於free 首期<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5dffad1417999aa1f265c50659b11e6aada03ff3","tid":1866530,"uid":103783,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-06T19:37:10.000Z","msg":"屎之戀<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"754e0358d2501f5c28bf2f6f53c52718961beaa1","tid":1866530,"uid":109629,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-06T22:27:13.000Z","msg":"睇都有得送<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9e699e7d813590e08df4a29796fe0ed23f79d1a0","tid":1866530,"uid":23445,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-06T22:28:44.000Z","msg":"「國難當前，套現買口罩」<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3b534d67d8a191a8658b3871ac72bbeca0ed1edd","tid":1866530,"uid":205016,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-06T22:41:09.000Z","msg":"愛滋戀"},{"pid":"dadc859